reviews.reviewbody: The story overall was good.  Sort of fairy tale like in that the poor youth marries a princess type.  I enjoyed the story and it is worth listening to.  The narration was a challenge but overall most of them did a good job.  I really prefer stories that only have one narrator but after awhile you get used to the various voices.
